Edge Rails

    cd rails
    rvm use gemset rails4
    railties/bin/rails new ~/Source/apps/blog --edge

Setting up Edge Rails

    git clone https://github.com/rails/rails.git
    cd rails
    bundle
    gem install bundler --pre
    bundle
    railties/bin/rails new ~/code/blog --edge -d postgresql

Run a script

    rails runner script.rb
